description:
Based on the hit PlayStation 3 game. Use your imagination to create detailed levels in the whimsical LittleBigPlanet universe, then share them with the world, and race through them with your friends. The critically acclaimed game LittleBigPlanet makes its way to the PSP, offering new SackBoy adventures with the same play, create, share experience for gamers on-the-go, in addition to brand new levels and environments specifically created for the platform. 

The emulator is Xbox360 controller compatible &amp; pre-configured.


System Requirements:

Core 2 duo 2.4GHz or higher.

nVidia GeForce GT 620 / ATI Radeon HD 5 series or higher.

3 Gig of ram or more.

Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8 32 or 64bit OS.


